This is a portable stun stick.

83
00:04:12,690 --> 00:04:14,310
I got you various sizes.

84
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:15,880
Keep this in your bag.

85
00:04:16,280 --> 00:04:17,310
Carry this with you.

86
00:04:17,620 --> 00:04:18,600
Why did you buy these?

87
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:19,670
Let me tell you,

88
00:04:19,950 --> 00:04:21,950
