89
00:04:22,650 --> 00:04:23,760
You should be cautious.

90
00:04:26,250 --> 00:04:27,710
Should I be wary of you?

91
00:04:27,980 --> 00:04:28,940
We're living together

92
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:30,320
under the same roof every day.

93
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:31,440
I haven't even said anything.

94
00:04:31,450 --> 00:04:32,490
And you bought these.

95
00:04:36,330 --> 00:04:37,800
Didn't you already have a crush on me?

96
00:04:37,950 --> 00:04:39,000
