I'd cling to you for life.

111
00:05:04,910 --> 00:05:05,840
You're fine?

112
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:07,940
You tricked me!

113
00:05:07,940 --> 00:05:08,790
You fool!

114
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:10,680
Good thing I dodged quickly.

115
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,920
Or I might've really gone blind.

116
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,160
But

117
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,950
